                        In my journey, I have developed a strong understanding of Unity's API and framework,
                        Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) concepts, and key game development techniques.
                        I have worked on various projects where I implemented game mechanics, physics, and
                        AI navigation systems, which allowed me to hone my skills in creating engaging and
                        immersive game experiences for console and mobile platforms.
                    </p>
